// GET REQUESTS
### Find all gardens
GET http://[::1]:3000/api/gardens

### Find garden by ID
GET http://[::1]:3000/api/gardens/6

### Find all plants
GET http://[::1]:3000/api/plants

### Find plant by ID
GET http://[::1]:3000/api/plants/691e4fa8aea4c898b5b90131

