//
// POST REQUESTS
### Add a new garden to the gardens collection
POST http://[::1]:3000/api/gardens
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Herb Garden",
  "location": "Botanical Garden",
  "description": "A garden with a variety of herbs",
  "dateCreated": "2023-04-15T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Add a new plant
POST http://[::1]:3000/api/plants/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Super Chili",
  "type": "Vegetable",
  "status": "Planted",
  "datePlanted": "2023-04-15T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Update an existing garden with corresponding ID
PATCH http://[::1]:3000/api/gardens/8
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Herb Garden",
  "location": "New Botanical Garden",
  "description": "An updated description for the herb garden."
}

### Update an existing garden with corresponding ID
PATCH http://[::1]:3000/api/plants/691e4fa8aea4c898b5b90131
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Tomato",
  "type": "Herb",
  "status": "Growing"
}

### Delete a garden
DELETE http://[::1]:3000/api/gardens/8

### Delete a plant
